_sText:
Since Sniper_Wars_V1 was a total failure. i made a V2 and this time it's much better. :)

Description: Spawn points are high in the sky. The different ends connected by a bridge. Cars on the bridge, Trees in the ground. Perfect place to snipe. A vent, to get in you need to go into 1 of the 2 portals. (1 on each side)

Note:Remember this was expanded on Sniper_warsV1.(also by me) but Sniper_wars_V2 has OZAMU to thank for some of the ideas.
